<hr>
This version is intended for Gun Game mod, and has no weapons or buyzones.
<hr>
This map was inspired by some of my favorite things from de_aztec.  It is set-up for a fast pace battle.  Both T and CT sides are equal.  This map offers both sniping, and close-range combat areas.  For info or suggestions for the final version visit: forums.solidsurf.info
